metadata.description:
Syryn Records Vol. I is the genesis NFT compilation album of the youth-run record label, Syryn Records.

Our mission at Syryn Records is to uplift and empower young women and gender-expansive youth interested in the music industry as artists and professionals. We run yearly internships where our participants support and nurture a group of youth artists and create a compilation record in support of our artists and program. This year's record features 11 talented female musicians, poets, songwriters, and producers.

Mastered by Tess Greenham.

Track list:

Salome Agbaroji - Make a Million

Geia - All Girls to the Front

a.kai - city lights

Bugz R Beautiful - Botfly Larvae

Zadie Jean - october

GeminiMusic - Let Me Go

Victorie - Lovesick

Gertrude - guilty

Raiesa - Why Should I?

Reiyn - Someday

gruel - ephermeral sun
metadata.name: Syryn Records Vol. I
